name: GATO 1
description:
Cisco is my youngest cat. I was very excited when I saw him lying in this cement mixing bowl.

That scene caught my attention so much that I went running to get the camera to record it. As time went by I saw that my other cats were also going to lie there to catch the afternoon sun.

I recorded each one of them and some hilarous scenes came out.
